<section class=3D"article-intro-text">
    <p>Although often used interchangeably, mass and weight are two distinc=
tly different units of measure.</p>
</section>

<section class=3D"article-info article-text">
    <div class=3D"col-section col-no-margin">
        <div class=3D"col-xs-6">
                            Data di pubblicazione: 12/01/2023
